data.description: 3BR, 2.5BA Custom Home w/2FP's & 4 Car Garage on 2 private acres w/ MTG @ 2.75% ASSUMABLE.  Gourmet Kitchen w/island, stainless, gas cooktop, 2 ovens, warming drawer opens to  breakfast & family room,  Dining Room & Vaulted Great Room - perfect for entertaining.  Office/library,  Owners BR w/ensuite BA has jetted soaking tub & oversized shower & lg walk-in closet.  2 car attached + 2 car detached garage & 2nd office.   2nd floor walk-up space for addtl rooms & storage.  2x6 construction,  GEOTHERMAL HVAC. Room 4 pool, pickle ball & addtl garage.  4 BR/3BA Septic.  NO HOA,  NO FEES.  Less than 2 miles to Bayhealth Hospital,  5 miles to DE Bay.  20 min. to Lewes & Rehoboth Beaches.   Offered $200K less than replacement !
